1-Spring Security is a framework that focuses on providing both authentication and authorization to Java applications
2- It is one of the most powerful and highly customizable authentication and access control frameworks in the Java ecosystem.

3-dependencies require for spring security app is spring-security-web and spring-security-config 

5-@EnableWebSecurity depicts, is used to enable SpringSecurity in our project. 

6-the addition of tge annotation@EnableWebSecurity provides Spring Security and also provides MVC integration support.
